{"_record_type": "fragment", "type": "expert_knowledge", "content": "to/Stats):** Should be crisp, monospace, or highly legible sans-serif.\n\n## 3. Spacing & The 8-Point Grid\nLet the UI breathe. Cramped components look like backend admin panels.\n*   Always use generous padding inside cards: `p-6` or `p-8`.\n*   Maintain vertical rhythm using large gaps: `gap-6`, `gap-8`, or `mb-12`.\n\n## 4. Buttons & Calls to Action\nButtons should be tactile and invite clicking.\n*   **Primary Buttons:** High contrast, rounded, with an inner glow or subtle box shadow.\n    *   *Tailwind Example:* `bg-white text-black font-semibold rounded-full px-6 py-2 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.3)] hover:scale-105 transition-transform`\n*   **Secondary Buttons:** Glassy, border-only.\n    *   *Tailwind Example:* `bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white rounded-full px-6 py-2 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors`\n\n## 5. Micro-Interactions\n*   Always apply `transition-all duration-300` to interactable elements.\n*   Use subtle scales (`hover:scale-[1.02]`) and opacity shifts.\n\n**MANDATE:** When tasked with building a UI, you must seamlessly integrate these utility classes and principles into the components. Make it look like a Dribbble portfolio piece.", "timestamp": "2026-03-26T12:43:36.044214", "embedding": [0.04320840165019035, 1.1084226369857788, -3.3735315799713135, -1.5769580602645874, 0.6696900725364685, -1.0160927772521973, 1.13278067111969, -0.22424648702144623, -0.396322637796402, -1.5910815000534058, 0.12415185570716858, 1.7104884386062622, 0.5497780442237854, 1.4001551866531372, 0.050601307302713394, -0.0032835283782333136, 0.4093609154224396, -1.0017120838165283, 0.7227590084075928, 0.6900913119316101, -0.4920803904533386, -0.7955312728881836, -0.27691343426704407, -1.038192629814148, 1.148972988128662, 1.885678768157959, 0.24867525696754456, 0.010726028122007847, -1.1652096509933472, -0.7307845950126648, 1.1756125688552856, -0.3741952180862427, -0.637698888778686